messageBody:
hello,
The recent activity here has prompted me to upload some files I've had lying about on my computer:
I've uploaded nouns and verbs spreadsheets plus a couple others in Malt's international QS project. These files bring the project to more or less what I set out to do from the start. Although the verb's -esp. the last 250- need a fair bit more work and there are quite a few hardbasket words that I haven't yet dealt with.
Also, I've uploaded the Alice-In-Wonderland progressive reading tutorials that I made a few years ago, since they are no longer on the web elsewhere.
